<p>If the buttons are disabled, their colour changes to gray and no hover or pointer event will occur.</p>

<h1 id="ghost-buttons">Ghost Buttons</h1>

<p>The ghost buttons are used for smaller elements in the project, e.g. to show idividual challenges or posts, or as a link to another page of the application. Like we did with the main buttons, we also mainly used <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">a</code>-tags and styled them accordingly. The only time we used a <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">button</code>-tag was on our filter form.</p>

